---
layout: base.njk
title: CodeMint · Personal Blog
description: 基于 GitHub Pages 的极简程序员风格技术博客
---
<main>
  <section class="hero container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Independent engineer · Build quietly · Think deeply</p>
    <h1>CodeMint</h1>
    <p class="sub-title">一个轻量、有质感、易维护的技术博客。像写代码一样写作：清晰、克制、可演进。</p>
    <a href="#latest" class="btn-primary">浏览最新文章</a>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="container section-card">
    <h2>风格说明</h2>
    <p>这套博客系统基于 Eleventy 与 GitHub Pages。你只需要写 Markdown，推送到 GitHub 后，Actions 会自动编译并发布到 <code>gh-pages</code> 分支。</p>
  </section>

  <section id="latest" class="container">
    <div class="section-title-row">
      <h2>最新文章</h2>
      <div class="tools-row">
        <label class="search-box">
          <span>⌕</span>
          <input id="post-search" type="search" placeholder="搜索文章" autocomplete="off" />
        </label>
        <div class="tag-row" id="tag-filter" role="list" aria-label="标签筛选"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="post-list" class="post-grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <article class="post-card" data-title="{{ post.data.title }}" data-excerpt="{{ post.data.description }}" data-tags="{{ post.data.tags | join(' ') }}">
          <p class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }} · {{ post.data.readTime or "5 min" }}</p>
          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          {% if post.data.tags %}
            <div class="tag-row" aria-label="文章标签">
              {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          <a class="btn-primary" href="{{ post.url | url }}">阅读全文 →</a>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
